  <p class="">TOY 1: BARN ANIMALS</p><p class="">We LOVE barn animals. We love naming or labeling the animals, making animal noises, and taking them out of these super cute barns! Another bonus is the fine motor skills kids work on while you model verbs for them! You can try words like “pull,” “open,” “on,” “in,” or “off.” Kids also love the surprise factor! Nothing makes kids giggle harder than when you make it a big deal with a big cheesy smile and ask “what is it?” before opening it up. </p>


  















































  

    
  
    

      

      
