  <p class="">TOY 2: BARN</p><p class="">You’ve got barn animals but where are they going to sleep?? You need a barn! These do come with more realistic barn animals but it’s another great way to make comparisons and work on size concepts like big versus small. You can work on singing songs like “Old McDonald” and use it for labeling the animals. Try it out!</p>


  















































  

    
  
    

      

      
